Deep Sepsis - Machine Learning for Health Project¶

Authors : Srinivasan Sivanandan, Sneha Desai, Daniel Dastoor, Angad Kalra¶

This script runs the following RNN models for early-sepsis prediction

  1. GRU
  2. GRU-M
  3. GRU-D
  4. LSTM
  5. LSTM-M
  6. LSTM-MD
